getBrowser

public static java.lang.String getBrowser(java.lang.String userAgent)
Return what type of browser is used based on the user-agent

Parameters:
userAgent -
Returns:
Returns the following values for Firefox, Internet Explorer, Chrome, and Safari:
- firefox
- internet explorer
- chrome
- safari

If the browser is not know, the error string "-1" will be returned
